<% content_for :title, "Transparent guarantee selection for investment firms" %>

<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <% name = 'Atlantico Hub' %>
    <h1><%= name.upcase! %></h1>
    <p>Transparent guarantee selection for investment firms</p>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modal-2">Schedule a meeting</button>

     <%= render "/shared/landing_modal" %>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="about text-center">
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <%= image_tag "icon_landing_info.svg", class:"images" %>
              <p> Easily keep track of your <strong>margin call</strong> in realtime </p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <%= image_tag "icon_landing_reorder.svg", class:"images" %>
              <p> Select your <strong>guarantees</strong> and choose how they will be used</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <%= image_tag "icon_landing_sendoff.svg", class:"images" %>
               <p> <strong>Integrate</strong> with your broker and enjoy the benefits of doing more with less</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="wrapper statement">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title">Don't let a great trading day be ruined by sloppy guarantee selection.</h2>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-6">
        <h2 class="title">Atlantico Hub was created to shed lights into the guarantee selection process.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <p>Very few people understands how the exchange calculates margin requirements and how the brokers use investment firm's assets to cover their margin calls.</p>
        <p>Our clients have visibilty over the margin requirements generated by their trades and the ability to pick and choose, beforehand, what they want to use as guarantee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <p>They can count on the <em>Atlantico Expert's</em> team to help them figure out how to better solve their guarantee selection problems and save a lot of money along the way.</p>
        <p>We love automation but, above all, we love people and we want everyone to have more free time to enjoy the important things in life.</p>
      </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
